#. [message]: speaker=Veomyr
#: data/campaigns/Secrets_of_the_Ancients/scenarios/02_Dark_Business.cfg:538
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "And why <i>seven</i> of us? Who wants to break into a cemetery that badly?"
